  "body": "In order to reduce the number of requests to infura, we have reduced the frequency and situations where the wallet is refreshed. \r\nWhen a user uses buy crypto, he expects to know he received his crypto as soon as he received them. \r\n\r\nWe should trigger refresh of the wallet after right after the user has used on buy crypto feature. \r\n\r\nnote: exact behaviour to be decided and described before implementation\r\n\r\ncc @cammellos ",
